What:
	‚Ä¢	Vesting structure: duration (3/4/5 yrs), cliff (e.g., 1 year), cadence (quarterly/yearly)
	‚Ä¢	Benchmark against peers

So What:
	‚Ä¢	Shows how ‚Äúvesting friction‚Äù affects employee value perception and retention
	‚Ä¢	Important for talent acquisition (e.g., competitive hiring in tech)

