	‚Ä¢	Could add segmentation by job role, level, or geo to reveal where design may be misaligned

2.3. Time-Based Wealth Accrual

What:
	‚Ä¢	Median equity value vesting over time for new hires
	‚Ä¢	Chart shows value + % vested

