3. Retention Risk Analytics

3.1. Attrition Spike at End of Vesting

What:
	‚Ä¢	Shows increase in attrition once original grant fully vests (esp. at 4-year mark)

So What:
	‚Ä¢	Exposes risk of front-loaded equity programs
	‚Ä¢	Justifies need for better refresh strategy or extended vesting designs

3.2. Wealth by Tenure

